MM5D - Growing house controlling and remote monitoring system
-------------------------------------------------------------

About software
--------------
  It is an internal software for MM5D Raspberry Pi based controlling and
monitoring equipment. It measures temperature and humidity, checks
programmable inputs, outputs and error lights. You can view actual status
with a browser application and administrate it with SSH client.

Requirements

  Hardware: Raspberry Pi 3 Model B
  Software: Raspberry Pi OS Lite operation system,
            Apache webserver,
            Perl,
            Python3.

How to get installer package for my OS?
---------------------------------------
a. Visit homepage (see later) to download installer packages:

  Raspbian OS: mm5d-sw-0.6-armhf.tar.gz

               mm5d-eec_0.6-1_armhf.deb
               mm5d-prepare_0.6-1_all.deb
               mm5d-sw_0.6-1_armhf.deb
               mm5d-web_0.6-1_all.deb

b. Download from Github

  $ git clone https://github.com/pozsarzs/mm5d-sw.git

c. Download from Debian repository

  set reporitory:
  $ sudo echo "deb http://www.pozsarzs.hu/deb/ ./" >> /etc/apt/sources.list
  $ sudo wget -q -O - http://www.pozsarzs.hu/deb/KEY.gpg | apt-key add -
  $ sudo apt-get update

  install:
  $ sudo apt-get install mm5d-prepare
  $ mm5d-prepare
  $ sudo apt-get install mm5d-sw mm5d-eec mm5d-web

